ink1">“虚拟人才学院”</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.l36285y9qk5p-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>招募时间：5月30日（星期四）-6月24日（星期一）12:00</p><p>运营 VTuber 团体“ <a href="https://twitter.com/nijisanji_app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nijisanji</a> ”的<a href="https://www.anycolor.co.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd.</a>已开始为人才发展项目“ <a href="https://vta.anycolor.co.jp/audition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Virtual Talent Academy (VTA)</a> ”招募新试镜。此次还将举办双人试镜。</p><p> VTA是ANYCOLOR利用其过去的发行知识来开发充当虚拟肝脏（VTuber）的主播的计划。到目前为止，Nijisanji 已经推出了 10 多个肝脏，包括毛茛属和 VOLTACTION。</p><p>此次，除了现有的VTA海选之外，还将举行双人海选。添加了附加条件，包括配对申请人关系密切。</p><p><a href="https://vta.anycolor.co.jp/audition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000909.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link2">《RK音乐》</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.virhx8uxyj3g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.virhx8uxyj3g-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.virhx8uxyj3g-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.virhx8uxyj3g-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.virhx8uxyj3g-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.virhx8uxyj3g-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>申请时间：6月1日（周六）18:30至6月30日（周日）23:59</p><p>专门从事VSinger的音乐制作公司<a href="https://rkmusic.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RK Music</a>将举办女性VSinger海选，招募新时代虚拟艺人。</p><p> RK Music是REALITY Studios旗下专门从事VSinger的音乐制作公司。 <a href="https://x.com/8HaChi_hacchi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HACHI</a> 、 <a href="https://x.com/KMNSTREET" target="_blank" rel="noopener">KMNZ</a> 、 <a href="https://x.com/vesperbell_info" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VESPERBELL</a>等VSinger都是会员。</p><p>通过考试的人将能够承担各种项目，例如发行原创音乐、在线现场表演、与观众一起现场表演、预订活动演出，并将获得音乐活动和 VSinger 发行活动的支持。</p><p><a href="https://rkmusic.jp/audition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000361.000021973.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">格力股份有限公司新闻稿</a></p><h2 id="link3">《下一个理想国》</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.zfnflhnaqemd-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.zfnflhnaqemd-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.zfnflhnaqemd-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.zfnflhnaqemd-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.mogur