2 id="link16"> 《Holostars》独家VTuber试镜</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-1024x630.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-1024x630.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-300x185.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-768x472.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/5421a6721ca51929f46e434cacc382bb-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-jpg.webp 1200w" width="1024" height="630" /></a></p><p>招聘期限：永久</p><p>男性VTuber团体“ <a href="https://www.holostars.tv/bosyu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Holo Stars</a> ”目前正在招募人才。招聘要求与上述Hololive相同。</p><p><a href="https://audition.hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>查看特别试镜页面。</p><h2 id="link17">如何通过试镜？</h2><p>如上所述，VTuber试镜的选择标准因公司而异，重要的问题是“你想做的活动是否符合公司的理念？”和“你是否符合公司的试镜条件？”</p><p>除此之外，还需要歌唱能力、舞蹈能力、语言能力、游戏能力、说话能力等各种能力。最近，对语言能力特别感兴趣的公司有所增加，如果能用英语或中文与粉丝自然地交谈，往往对试镜有利。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2022/01/202201021118082000-300x169.jpg"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal">如果我想成为一名VTuber我该怎么办？ 必要事项、注意事项等基础知识汇总</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">很多人在观看每天活跃的VTuber的直播和视频后都会想：“我也想尝试一下！”然而，有很多事情我不太明白，比如我需要做什么才能出道，我首先需要什么。</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTuber</span> <span class=